Grouping of similar user stories:
1. User story: As a new user, I want to create an email account with my preferred username and password.
2. User story: As an existing user, I want to set up email forwarding to another email address.
3. User story: As an existing user, I want to configure email filters to manage incoming emails effectively.
4. User story: As an existing user, I want to set up an out-of-office automatic reply message.
5. User story: As an existing user, I want to sync my email account with third-party applications like calendar and contacts.
6. User story: As an existing user, I want to enable email encryption for secure communication.

Based on the above user stories, the feature "Email Account Setup" can include the following functionalities:
- Account creation with customization options
- Email forwarding setup
- Email filter configuration
- Out-of-office message setup
- Integration with third-party applications
- Email encryption feature.

