Feature Name: Email Categorization and Labeling
Description: This feature enables users to organize and categorize their emails effectively based on user-defined criteria.

Key Functionality:
1. Rule Creation: Users can create custom rules to automatically categorize incoming emails into specific folders or labels.
2. Labeling Options: Users have the flexibility to assign color-coded labels to emails based on keywords, sender information, or other specified criteria.
3. Automated Categorization: Implement automated algorithms that categorize incoming emails according to predefined rules or user-defined settings.

User Benefit: By utilizing this feature, users can efficiently manage their email inbox, save time on manual sorting, and ensure important emails are prioritized and easily accessible. It enhances organization and productivity in handling email communications.

