Acceptance Criteria:
- User can access a compose email screen.
- User can enter recipient email addresses, subject, and email body.
- User can send the email successfully.
Estimated Effort: 10 hours
Dependencies: N/A

Task ID: 3
Task Title: Integrate Reply and Compose Email Functionalities
Related User Story: As a user, I want the reply and compose email functionalities to work seamlessly with the existing email routing system.
