=== Final Email Router Project Plan ===

## Workflow Step: User Story 1: As a user, I want to be able to login to the Email Router platform securely using my email and password.
As a user, I want to be able to login to the Email Router platform securely using my email and password so that I can access the system and perform my tasks without compromising security.

## Workflow Step: Feature: User Authentication
Feature Name: User Authentication
Description: The User Authentication feature focuses on ensuring secure access to user accounts through various authentication methods.
Key Functionality: 
- User account creation with a username and password
- Secure login process
- Password reset functionality
- Account information update
- Suspicious activity notifications
User Benefit: Enhances account security and user experience by providing secure access and robust account management capabilities.

## Workflow Step: Task: Implement authentication system with email and password verification
1. Set up a user database to store user information securely.
2. Create API endpoints for user registration and login.
3. Implement email verification process for new user registration.
4. Create password hashing functionality for secure storage.
5. Develop verification logic to confirm user identity during login process.
6. Implement password reset functionality for users who forget their passwords.
7. Test the authentication system thoroughly to ensure security and functionality.
8. Document the authentication system setup and usage for future reference.

## Workflow Step: User Story 2: As a user, I want to be able to set up email accounts to be monitored by the Email Router.
Feature Name: Email Account Setup
Description: This feature enables users to seamlessly set up and manage email accounts for monitoring by the Email Router.
Key Functionality: Users can add, configure, and delete email accounts, set up monitoring preferences, and receive notifications for incoming emails.
User Benefit: By utilizing this feature, users can efficiently manage their email accounts, ensuring timely monitoring and response to important emails, ultimately enhancing productivity and communication efficiency.

## Workflow Step: Feature: Email Account Setup
Grouping of similar user stories:
1. User story: As a new user, I want to create an email account with my preferred username and password.
2. User story: As an existing user, I want to set up email forwarding to another email address.
3. User story: As an existing user, I want to configure email filters to manage incoming emails effectively.
4. User story: As an existing user, I want to set up an out-of-office automatic reply message.
5. User story: As an existing user, I want to sync my email account with third-party applications like calendar and contacts.
6. User story: As an existing user, I want to enable email encryption for secure communication.

Based on the above user stories, the feature "Email Account Setup" can include the following functionalities:
- Account creation with customization options
- Email forwarding setup
- Email filter configuration
- Out-of-office message setup
- Integration with third-party applications
- Email encryption feature.

