## Workflow Step: Feature: Email Tracking
Feature: Email Tracking
Description: This feature allows users to track the activity of their sent emails, including when they were opened, if attachments were downloaded, and when links were clicked.
Key Functionality: Provides real-time notifications for email opens, attachment downloads, and link clicks. Displays a log of email interaction times.
User Benefit: Users can ensure timely communication by knowing when their emails are viewed and accessed, improving follow-ups and engagement with recipients.

Feature: Detailed Email Open Time
Description: Users can view the exact time their email was opened by the recipient, providing precise information on when the email was accessed.
